{"can_edit": true, "from": {"name": "Peter Boyd", "id": "1312089751"}, "subject": "General Purpose Linux Links Every Penguinisto Should Know", "updated_time": "2012-06-20T19:39:35+0000", "can_delete": true, "created_time": "2012-06-20T19:39:35+0000", "message": "<p>This is a page for general links which will work in any distribution.  It assumes you&#039;ve already got Linux installed and you know about  general care and feeding of your distribution of choice.\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>GETTING HELP: Have a question? Type &quot;man subject&quot; first on the  command line. Q to quit. Replace subject with what you&#039;re interested in  suchas &quot;man apache&quot; or &quot;man cron&quot;. --help also produces the expected set  of results.\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>BASH programming intro:\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftldp.org%2FHOWTO%2FBash-Prog-Intro-HOWTO.html&amp;h=DAQHpm5Br&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/tldp.org\\/HOWTO\\/Bash-Prog-Intro-HOWTO.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Ftldp.org\\u00252FHOWTO\\u00252FBash-Prog-Intro-HOWTO.html&amp;h=DAQHpm5Br&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://tldp.org/HOWTO/Bash-Prog-Intro-HOWTO.html</a></p>\n<p>BASH is the general purpose Linux shell which has become the standard  of the community. If you&#039;re coming from ksh or ash, it will feel  similar. You can make your life a lot easier if you learn how to script  one offs on the command line.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>PERL programming intro:\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fperldoc.perl.org%2Fperlintro.html&amp;h=5AQG7RXwu&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/perldoc.perl.org\\/perlintro.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fperldoc.perl.org\\u00252Fperlintro.html&amp;h=5AQG7RXwu&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://perldoc.perl.org/perlintro.html</a></p>\n<p>PERL became the crossover language for a lot of people (including  myself) where we had to write-once-run-everywhere among disparate Linux  systems. Perl is available on almost all *NIX similar boxes. If it&#039;s not  written in BASH, it&#039;s probably written in PERL. (If you&#039;re wondering  &quot;Can I script for a Mac? Look for perl).</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><a href=\"Look.org:\">Look.org:</a>\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkde-look.org%2F&amp;h=PAQHYV_Eo&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/kde-look.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fkde-look.org\\u00252F&amp;h=PAQHYV_Eo&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://kde-look.org/</a> and\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgnome-look.org%2F&amp;h=LAQHCN4J-&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/gnome-look.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fgnome-look.org\\u00252F&amp;h=LAQHCN4J-&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://gnome-look.org/</a></p>\n<p>Think someone&#039;s theme is cool? Check out these links to pimp your penguin.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Editing Files:\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eng.hawaii.edu%2FTutor%2Fvi.html&amp;h=xAQGooOvI&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.eng.hawaii.edu\\/Tutor\\/vi.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.eng.hawaii.edu\\u00252FTutor\\u00252Fvi.html&amp;h=xAQGooOvI&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.eng.hawaii.edu/Tutor/vi.html</a> OR\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gnu.org%2Fsoftware%2Femacs%2F&amp;h=wAQFgt__w&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.gnu.org\\/software\\/emacs\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.gnu.org\\u00252Fsoftware\\u00252Femacs\\u00252F&amp;h=wAQFgt__w&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/</a></p>\n<p>I prefer vi, but discussions on this topic is the stuff of legend.  Both vi and emacs are installed in major *NIX systems. Pick one, learn  it and love it.</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>What&#039;s the code look like OR where did all this come from:\u00a0<a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gentoo.org%2F&amp;h=ZAQGGXqcX&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.gentoo.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.gentoo.org\\u00252F&amp;h=ZAQGGXqcX&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.gentoo.org/</a></p>\n<p>The last living source distro with any serious community (slackware -  you break my heart). Want to tune the distro to 11? Read up. Think  building a kernel is kool? You can probably learn here. Glutton for  punishment or simply want to have compiler races? Great! Think Linux  would run awesome on your ATARI 800? Awesome!</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>You have a problem that you cannot fix?: Try to get help from <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linuxquestions.org%2F&amp;h=PAQHYV_Eo&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.linuxquestions.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.linuxquestions.org\\u00252F&amp;h=PAQHYV_Eo&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.linuxquestions.org/</a> or from your distro&#039;s main site forums section...</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Common Ubuntu Package Problems and Fixes:</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaketecheasier.com%2Ffix-ubuntu-update-errors%2F2011%2F12%2F16&amp;h=JAQG8imEU&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/maketecheasier.com\\/fix-ubuntu-update-errors\\/2011\\/12\\/16&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fmaketecheasier.com\\u00252Ffix-ubuntu-update-errors\\u00252F2011\\u00252F12\\u00252F16&amp;h=JAQG8imEU&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://maketecheasier.com/fix-ubuntu-update-errors/2011/12/16</a></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Technical sites I read:</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slashdot.org%2F&amp;h=VAQF8LMzW&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.slashdot.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.slashdot.org\\u00252F&amp;h=VAQF8LMzW&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.slashdot.org</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kuro5hin.org%2F&amp;h=qAQFXm5_7&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.kuro5hin.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.kuro5hin.org\\u00252F&amp;h=qAQFXm5_7&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.kuro5hin.org</a> (archives have good stuff)</p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ycombinator.com%2F&amp;h=dAQFrTpR7&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"